{"tid":450917,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)曬撚氣1-2","createTime":"2017-10-28T15:34:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-28T18:15:59.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"84e68c9ceb869b370c90c0eb243f78c455deaaaf","tid":450917,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:34:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=oQ6o364sYYoZTY8FvzS16Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=7bf221dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> V台入佢主頁睇先比較順<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=oQ6o364sYYoZTY8FvzS16Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=edcd6c45\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c2/鬼魅山房2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc2%2F%E9%AC%BC%E9%AD%85%E5%B1%B1%E6%88%BF2.jpg&h=9d47039a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/5/57/Silent_hill.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F5%2F57%2FSilent_hill.jpg&h=2ea57286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.蘿絲（Rose Da Silva）自小收養的女兒雪倫（Sharon Da Silva）患有夢遊症且多次提及小鎮『沉默之丘』。為尋求答案，蘿絲不顧丈夫克里斯席瓦（Christopher Da Silva）的反對於一天晚上帶著雪倫前往沉默之丘。在接近小鎮時二人被女警西碧兒（Cybil Bennett）追捕（因懷疑蘿絲企圖遺棄雪倫），蘿絲於驅車擺脫追捕時突然看見一女孩在路上出現，為閃避而撞上路邊失去知覺。蘿絲於醒來時發現雪倫竟已失蹤，白霧籠罩著一切，無數灰燼從天上持續地飄落。<br />\n<br />\n蘿絲為尋回雪倫而在荒無一人的街上尋找，除首次經歷沉默之丘表世界（Fog world）和裏世界（Otherworld）的交替，也遇到一名為妲麗亞（Dahlia Gillespie）的婦人。妲麗亞告訴蘿絲其女兒亞萊莎（Alessa Gillespie）被村民虐待，並在看見雪倫的相片後認為她就是亞萊莎。蘿絲擺脫妲麗亞後回到車子欲聯絡丈夫但遇上西碧兒，西碧兒發現雪倫失蹤後拘捕蘿絲帶回警署，但在徒步回程時發現道路被斷崖取代。二人只得繼續在鎮上尋找出路...<br />\n<br />\n2.海瑟梅森和父親哈利梅森一直以來都在躲避不明力量的恐怖追殺。她18歲生日當晚，在夢魘纏身和父親神秘失蹤的詭譎情況下，海瑟發現自己原來從未瞭解「真正的自己」。隨著啟示錄的指引，她踏入了一個危機四伏、狂暴絕倫，可能令她永世不得脫身的邪惡世界&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n11 45PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=oQ6o364sYYoZTY8FvzS16Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=9e236cd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=oQ6o364sYYoZTY8FvzS16Bxs2jlPaATBKfveiEY0UFo%3D&h=281a166d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3efc3c71dd8fba5406af65a3cf33a3403707c5fd","tid":450917,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1adfd338e2b510f6171e711a214ba7f8d8487a32","tid":450917,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T15:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2815415b2cb1c133f0fb35c8fa9564c86e875b0a","tid":450917,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-28T16:13:18.0